Data availability

            The global daily PM2.5 data39 are available from MERRA-2 (https://doi.org/10.5067/KLICLTZ8EM9D). The global daily wildfire-PM2.5 data43 are available from FMI (https://doi.org/10.23728/fmi-b2share.722bb9d1937548908d2b6c1cfd9f8e5d). The population data48 are available from LandScan (https://doi.org/10.48690/1529167). The global residential air exchange rate data45 are available from Han et al.45. The baseline DALY rate data24 are available from Institute for Health Metrics and Evaluation (https://vizhub.healthdata.org/gbd-results/). Source data are provided with this paper.
          Code availability

            Computational methods and statistical analyses are described in the article. The code used for the analyses in this study is publicly available on Zenodo via https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.18767443 (ref. 56).
